data.description: Lovely 4 bedroom, 2 bath home in Stallion Springs that looks like new (built in 2020). It has all the popular, modern amenities such as LVP flooring, quartz counters in the kitchen and bathrooms, white cabinets, stainless-steel appliances, decorative tile backsplash and more. The gourmet kitchen opens into the spacious family room which has an impressive, stacked rock fireplace. There is a separate dining room and a kitchen dining area. The primary suite has plenty of room, dual vanities, a walk-in closet and sliding glass doors to the back yard. The back yard is completely fenced and has a large concrete patio and RV parking area. The kids will love the fact that the property is walking distance from a park with pickle ball courts, a basketball court and a baseball field. This home provides the conveniences of a modern home in a beautiful country setting.
